\v 2 Ngoba ulaka luyasibulala isiwula, lomhawu ubulale isiphukuphuku\x + 6.2.\x*.
\v 3 Mina ngibone isiwula sigxila, kodwa ngahle ngaqalekisa indawo yaso yokuhlala\x + Hlab. 37.35,36. Jer. 12.2,3. Zaga 24.30.\x*.
\v 4 Abantwana baso bakhatshana losindiso\x + Hlab. 119.155.\x*, bachothozwa esangweni\x + 29.7. Hlab. 127. 5 Zaga 22.22. Josh. 20.4. Ruthe 4.1,2.\x*, njalo kungekho umkhululi\x + Hlab. 109.12.\x*.
\v 5 Osivuno saso olambileyo uyasidla, esithatha lemeveni\x + Zaga 22.5.\x*, lomphangi uginya inotho yaso\x + 18.9.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba usizi kaluveli ethulini, lenhlupheko kayihlumi emhlabathini.
\v 7 Kube kanti umuntu uzalelwe inhlupheko njengoba inhlansi ziqhatshela phezulu\x + 14.1. Gen. 3.17-19.\x*.
