\v 8 Kodwa mina bengizadinga uNkulunkulu, lakuNkulunkulu bengizabeka udaba lwami.
\v 9 Owenza izinto ezinkulu lezingelakuhlolwa, imimangaliso engelakubalwa\x + 9.10. 37.5. Hlab. 40.5.72.18. Roma 11.33.\x*.
\v 10 Onika izulu ebusweni bomhlaba, athumele amanzi ebusweni bamaphandle\x + 28.26. Hlab. 65.9,10. 147.8. Jer. 5.24. 10.13. 14.22. 51.16. Seb. 14.17. Hlab. 104.10.\x*,
