\v 12 Uchitha amacebo abalobuqili, ukuze izandla zabo zingenzi cebo\x + Neh. 4.15. Hlab. 33.10. Isa. 8.10.\x*.
\v 13 Ubamba abahlakaniphileyo ebuqilini babo\x + 18.7. 1 Kor. 3.19.\x*, ukuze icebo labangaqondanga liwiselwe phansi\x + Zaga 8.8.\x*.
\v 14 Bahlangana lomnyama emini, baphumputhe phakathi kwemini njengebusuku\x + 12.25. Dute. 28.29.\x*.
\v 15 Kodwa ukhulula umyanga enkembeni, emlonyeni wabo, lesandleni solamandla\x + Hlab. 35.10.\x*.
\v 16 Ngakho umyanga ulethemba, lobubi buzavala umlomo wabo\x + Hlab. 107.42.\x*.
