\v 17 Khangela, ubusisiwe lowomuntu uNkulunkulu amlayayo\x + Hlab. 94.12.\x*; ngakho ungadeleli\x + Zaga 3.11.\x* ukukhuza kukaSomandla\x + Gen. 17.1.\x*.
\v 18 Ngoba yena uzwisa ubuhlungu, abuye abophe; uyalimaza, lezandla zakhe ziyapholisa\x + Dute. 32.39. Isa. 30.26.\x*.
\v 19 Uzakukhulula\x + Hlab. 34.19. 91.3.\x* enhluphekweni eziyisithupha\x + Zaga 24.16. Mat. 18.21. 2 Kho. 7.13.\x*, lakweziyisikhombisa\x + Zaga 24.16. Mat. 18.21. 2 Kho. 7.13.\x* ububi kabuyikukuthinta\x + Hlab. 91.10.\x*.
