\v 22 Uzahleka\x + 39.7,18. 41.29.\x* incithakalo lendlala\x + 30.3.\x*, njalo kawuyikwesaba izilo zomhlaba\x + Isa. 11.8,9. 35.9. 65.25. Hez. 34.25.\x*.
\v 23 Ngoba uzakuba lesivumelwano lamatshe eganga\x + Hos. 2.18.\x*, lezilo zeganga zizakuba lokuthula lawe\x + Hos. 2.18.\x*.
\v 24 Njalo uzakwazi ukuthi ithente lakho lilokuthula, uzakwethekela indawo yakho yokuhlala ungasweli lutho.
\v 25 Uzakwazi futhi ukuthi inzalo yakho izakuba nengi, lembewu yakho njengotshani bomhlaba.
\v 26 Uzafika engcwabeni lakho usuluphele, njengenqumbi zamabele zisenyuka ngesikhathi sawo.
\v 27 Khangela lokhu, sesikuhlolile; kunjalo. Kuzwe, uzazele wena.
